ed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### I did this\n\n\r\nThere was an issue in Tarantool [^1] due to regression in libcurl (#11769), it was reported on 23 Aug, 2023. Issue was fixed in upstream on 4 Sept, 2023 and fix was confirmed by our tests for Tarantool. Unfortunately, this fix was ruined by refactoring made in commit d7b6ce64ce0ad (\"lib: replace readwrite with write_resp\") [3] on 1 Dec 2023, and now it is reproduced again. Then it was fixed in #13260 and regression test was added within fix. However, commit 270a25c011367f6300d5c01497fb1f23527458f4 that fixes #13337 broke fix again.\r\n\r\n- Reproducer for Tarantool is described in [^1]\r\n- Reproducer for libcurl is described in #11769, I'm not sure, it is worth to duplicate it here\r\n\r\n[^0]: https://curl.se/mail/lib-2024-03/0060.html\r\n[^1]: https://github.com/tarantool/tarantool/issues/9086\n\n### I expected the following\n\nFix of the original problem.\n\n### curl/libcurl version\n\n270a25c011367f6300d5c01497fb1f23527458f4\n\n### operating system\n\nUbuntu 22.04 amd64","closed_by":{"login":"bagder","id":177011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE3NzAxMQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/177011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder","html_url":"https://github.com/bagder","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bagder/received_events","type":"User"